<h1 style="text-align: center" class="display-3">Who is UNICEF?</h1>


<p class="lead" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 10px" >UNICEF is an international organisation
    that strives for the betterment of life for children around the globe. Over the last few decades,
    they have made huge progress in affecting the the lives of children either indirectly through moving issues
    into the agenda of policy makers, or directly through the actions of community protection  mechanisms.
    <br>UNICEF's noble actions truly hold true to their mission statement, which is as follows:</p>


